### Non-blocking notes (deferred)
- Formatting (multi-line vs single-line `invalidateCache(...)` call) is purely stylistic and not worth raising until the correctness issues above are resolved.
- Separately (out of scope for this PR): `invalidateCache` mutates `store` while iterating its `keys()`. It happens to be safe for `Map` in practice, but collecting keys first would be more defensive.

